text: Gorodetskoye () is a rural locality (a selo) in Beketovsky Selsoviet, Yermekeyevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 153 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 30 km from Yermekeyevo, 5 km from Beketovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yermekeyevsky District
title: Gorodetskoye, Republic of Bashkortostan
